        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Freedom Financing Act </b></p> <p>This bill restricts certain banks, credit&nbsp;unions,&nbsp;and payment card networks&nbsp;from refusing to do business with a person based on reputational considerations.</p>]]></text>
